Kirby 21 MRICloud Data

Kirby-21-MRICloud-Data.Rd

A dataset containing correlation data for 20 subjects from Kennedy Krieger. This data is the kirby 21 data set that can be found here.. The data contain 2 techinical visits. the data include:

  • cor.txt Correlations from resting state fMRI.

  • DIT_ma.csv Diffusion tensor imaging summary measures

  • *_corrected_stats.txt Volumetric output

  • *_stats.txt Volumetric output

  • matrix_air.txt

  • matrix.txt

  • multilevel_lookup_table.txt

  • tc.txt functional MRI resting state time courses

  • z_cor.txt Fisher's Z transformed correlations for resting state fMRI.

Format

Subject directories in two visits containing text files with raw MRIcloud output
